"location": "Leipzig",
"title": "SOLUTION ENGINEER (M/F/X)",
"description": "<p>True to the motto: \"Our know-how - Your solution\" QUAJOO GmbH has been inspiring its customers since 2008 with its versatile expertise as an IT service provider in the areas of software development, software architecture, project management and consulting as well as the operation of scalable systems.</p>\n<p>QUAJOO helps retail brands in Europe achieve their digital transformation at the highest level. We integrate in-store, inventory, and eCommerce solutions with modern technology and retail experience.</p>\n<p>To ensure competent implementation, we are looking for a Solution Engineer (M/F/X):</p>\n<h2>Your tasks:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>As a determined and communicative team member with a passion for new technologies, you will be significantly contributing to the further development of existing customer projects</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You will develop new platforms using state-of-the-art technology stacks or are responsible for their relaunch</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You will contribute to the expansion of customer-specific CI and CD processes, the recording, and evaluation of new requirements in cooperation with the customers as well as the installation and testing of version and security updates</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Thanks to your highly analytical and problem-solving thinking, you also ensure the smooth operation of the staging and production environments</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>This profile will win us over:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>You gained programming experience in one of the following technologies: C#, Java, TypeScript/ JavaScript, PHP or Python</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You feel secure in dealing with databases, and you are an all-rounder in frontend as well as backend programming</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Your professional experience allows you to introduce your knowledge of object-oriented programming, know-how in the area of CI/CD and systems such as Gitlab or Github</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>You will be able to manage your daily business thanks to your experienced handling of RESTful backend services</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Your knowledge of Microservices (Docker, Kubernetes), Azure/AWS, Angular/React, Magento, Test Automation (E2E, Unit Tests) and also Retail/eCommerce experience (POS, Payment) complete your profile, it’s a plus</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>That's what QUAJOO offers you:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Participation in a continuously growing company with flat hierarchies and agile development processes</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Exciting projects with modern technologies and a lot of potential for your personal development</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>A job in the city center of Leipzig</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Your work will, of course, be reasonably salaried and additionally rewarded in case of project success and goal achievement</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Regular team events as well as free snacks, coffee, etc. will ensure your future-all-round carefree package</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Did we convince you?</h2>\n<p>We are looking forward to receiving your application via mail: <a href=\"mailto:jobs@quajoo.de\">jobs@quajoo.de</a>.</p>\n",
"how_to_apply": "<p>via mail: <a href=\"mailto:jobs@quajoo.de\">jobs@quajoo.de</a>.</p>\n",
