"created_at": "Wed Jun 19 11:37:44 UTC 2019",
"company": "BASF Services Europe GmbH",
"company_url": "http://www.basf.com",
"location": "Berlin",
"title": "Developer/ Consultant Automation of Business Processes & UIPath (m/f/d)",
"description": "<h2>\n<strong>Job Field:</strong> IT / Information Management</h2>\n<h2>\n<strong>Location:</strong> Berlin, DE</h2>\n<h2>\n<strong>Company:</strong> BASF Services Europe GmbH</h2>\n<h2>\n<strong>Job Type:</strong> Permanent</h2>\n<h2>\n<strong>Job ID:</strong> EN57924440_ONLE_1</h2>\n<p>We are the world's leading chemical company because we offer intelligent solutions for our customers and for a sustainable future. We connect and develop people with diverse talents all over the world. For you, this means a variety of ways to advance. Not only your performance but also your personality matter to us, without regard to gender, age, origin, sexual orientation, disability or belief. At BASF, careers develop from opportunities.</p>\n<p>BASF Services Europe GmbH, located in the heart of Berlin, is a shared service center providing a wide range of services for the BASF Group throughout Europe. As an international team of 2,000 employees from over 50 countries, we bring together know-how in the fields of finance, controlling, HR, procurement, product safety and digitalization. We value teamwork, engagement and embrace Diversity &amp; Inclusion.</p>\n<p>Learn more about the SSC at: <a href=\"https://www.on.basf.com/EuropeanSSC\">https://www.on.basf.com/EuropeanSSC</a></p>\n<h2><strong>What you can expect</strong></h2>\n<p>Become part of our Business Reporting Unit and work on digitization topics for the global finance and controlling community from process optimization to recommendations for action from big data analysis.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>As part of the process optimization, you take over the consulting and development of automation solutions using for example UIPath RPA or other script solutions.</li>\n<li>Furthermore, you are responsible for the functionality of the automation solutions after implementation by defining suitable measures.</li>\n<li>As part of a holistic knowledge management you foster the sharing of information while expanding and sharing your own knowledge within the global digitalization community.</li>\n<li>You contribute to challenging projects in the unit, supporting with process consulting while receiving comprehensive insights into the financial and controlling processes of BASF.</li>\n<li>Unfold your knowledge in our international team and use the opportunity to experiment with new technologies.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>What we expect</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You have successfully completed your studies in (economic) computer science or a comparable education and gained initial professional experience in IT.</li>\n<li>You are proficient in common object oriented programming languages such as Python and R, ideally you already have experience in the area of RPA.</li>\n<li>In addition to your strong affinity to numbers, you have gained strong analytical abilities in the field of process analysis or statistics during your studies or professional career.</li>\n<li>You are passionate about new technologies and enjoy working with colleagues and business partners on common solutions.</li>\n<li>You convince us by your independent way of working and high level of commitment, without losing sight of the common goals.</li>\n<li>Please state your salary expectations and your earliest starting date in the motivational letter.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>We offer</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In our Berlin office, you will be given the opportunity to shape your own personal development, while making a profound impact on our European services.</li>\n<li>Receiving on-the-job training through our \"Buddy System\", you will be able to benefit from flexible working hours.</li>\n<li>As part of our dynamic team, you have the chance to engage and experience diversity &amp; inclusion on a daily basis as well as contribute your ideas to the worldwide BASF network.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>Interested?</strong></h2>\n<p>Apply now by using <a href=\"https://basfse.redirect.your-jobresponse.com/developer_consultant_automation_of_business_processes_uipath_m_f_d_berlin/250107/V819/anwenden\">this link</a></p>\n<p><strong>Join the best team with more than 110,000 other minds to connect with globally. Explore your BASF career options at <a href=\"on.basf.com/mycareer\">on.basf.com/mycareer</a></strong></p>\n",
"how_to_apply": "<p><a href=\"https://basfse.redirect.your-jobresponse.com/developer_consultant_automation_of_business_processes_uipath_m_f_d_berlin/250107/V819/anwenden\">Click here to apply!</a></p>\n",
