"created_at": "Tue Jun 18 20:29:18 UTC 2019",
"company": "Public Broadcasting Service",
"company_url": "http://www.pbs.org/jobs",
"location": "Arlington, VA",
"title": "Sr. Android Engineer",
"description": "<p><strong>Senior Android Engineer</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Team:</strong> Product Development</p>\n<p><strong>Status:</strong> Full-time/Regular/Exempt</p>\n<p>This onsite position is located at PBS Headquarters in Arlington, VA.</p>\n<p>Do you want to make the world a better place while working with the latest in mobile technologies? Are you looking for a job that is challenging but also allows a work-life balance? Then join our small but nimble team responsible for streaming content to millions of viewers.</p>\n<p><strong>We Have:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Two top-rated, editor's choice, Android and OTT applications.</li>\n<li>A fantastic work-life balance environment.</li>\n<li>A team of outstanding developers, Product Managers, QA, and UI/UX designers all versed in a wide variety of technologies, who love to share knowledge.</li>\n<li>An open mind for new ideas and methodologies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>You Have:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>A love of mobile development.</li>\n<li>5+ years of experience in Java, Kotlin, and the Android Platform.</li>\n<li>Experience in Automated testing.</li>\n<li>A personality that enjoys collaborating with fun people.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>You Might Wow Us With:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Knowledge of Google Analytics, Firebase, and RESTful Web Services.</li>\n<li>Knowledge of the Realm database.</li>\n<li>Streaming video experience.</li>\n<li>Any amazing apps of your own.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you want to work with a group of people who are smart and get things done, please start by clicking the button below. Please include some samples of your work in your application: code, blog posts, and links to personal or professional sites.</p>\n<p><strong>PBS is an Equal Opportunity Employer of Minorities, Women, Protected Veterans, and Individuals with Disabilities</strong></p>\n",
"how_to_apply": "<p>Apply online: <a href=\"https://jobapply.page.link/1kXm\">https://jobapply.page.link/1kXm</a></p>\n",
